sentences: Thorsten Quaeschning (born 23 February 1977) is a German musician.
He is the current bandleader of Tangerine Dream which he joined in 2005.
Thorsten Quaeschning was born in 1977 in Berlin within a classically trained music-loving family.
Afterwards, he began to tour with Tangerine Dream behind the scenes in 2003 before joining them two years later.
